body.p:
Commonwealth of Kentucky Plaintiff
against } On sums in For: Bail Bond
Nathan Bibb & others Defendants

The Defts Nathan Bibb, George W Dupee & General Douglass having been duly Summoned and failing to answer, it is ordered & adjudged that the Plaintiff recover of said Bibb, Dupee & Douglass, Fifty Dollars, the Debt in the Summons mentioned & also her costs herein --
A copy att Jno B Norton cfcc
